ADDIS ABABA, Ethiopia, February 25, 2019/APO Group/ -- 
                                                        
                            Please join us on February 27, 2019 at 4:45PM for an online video press briefing with the Under Secretary of State for Political Affairs, Ambassador David Hale. Under Secretary Hale will discuss his recent travel to Africa and U.S. Africa policy. 



Broadcast-quality video and audio files will be made available for clipping in media reports at the conclusion of the briefing.



DETAILS:

Speaker: David Hale, Under Secretary of State for Political Affairs
